{%- comment -%}
  Return / Refund Policy — 60-day money-back guarantee
  Friendly, clear, confidence-building.
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="policy-page return-page">
  <div class="policy-page__inner page-width">

    <span class="section-eyebrow">Returns &amp; Refunds</span>
    <h1 class="section-heading">60-Day Money-Back Guarantee</h1>
    <p class="policy-page__intro">We believe in the [BRAND]™ belt — and we want you to believe in it too. That's why we offer a full 60-day money-back guarantee. If it doesn't work for you, you get your money back. Simple as that.</p>
    <p class="policy-page__updated">Last updated: {{ 'now' | date: '%B %d, %Y' }}</p>

    <div class="policy-content">

      <div class="policy-highlight-box">
        <div class="policy-highlight-box__icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none">
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="22" stroke="#2ecc71" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M16 24l6 6 10-10" stroke="#2ecc71" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Our Promise</h3>
          <p>Try the [BRAND]™ belt for 60 days. If you don't feel a meaningful difference in your pain, we'll give you a full refund — no questions asked, no hoops to jump through.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <div class="policy-steps">
          <div class="policy-step">
            <div class="policy-step__number">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Use It for Up to 60 Days</h3>
              <p>Give the belt a real chance. We recommend using it daily for at least 2–4 weeks to experience the full benefits of infrared light therapy. Most users notice meaningful improvement within this time.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="policy-step">
            <div class="policy-step__number">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Contact Us</h3>
              <p>If you're not satisfied, simply email us at <strong>support@[brand].com</strong> within 60 days of receiving your order. Let us know what happened — we may be able to help troubleshoot first.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="policy-step">
            <div class="policy-step__number">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Return &amp; Get Your Refund</h3>
              <p>We'll email you a prepaid return label. Ship the belt back to us, and once we receive it, your full refund will be processed within <strong>5–7 business days</strong>.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Return Conditions</h2>
        <ul class="policy-list">
          <li>Returns must be initiated within <strong>60 days</strong> of the delivery date.</li>
          <li>The product must be returned in its original packaging (or reasonable equivalent).</li>
          <li>The product should be in used but functional condition — we expect you to try it. That's the whole point.</li>
          <li>Refunds are issued to the original payment method.</li>
          <li>Shipping costs for the original order are non-refundable (if applicable).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Damaged or Defective Products</h2>
        <p>If your [BRAND]™ belt arrives damaged or has a manufacturing defect, contact us immediately at <strong>support@[brand].com</strong>. We'll send you a replacement at no cost — no need to return the damaged unit first. Include a photo of the damage when you reach out so we can resolve it quickly.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Exchanges</h2>
        <p>We don't currently offer direct exchanges. If you'd like a different product, simply return your current order for a refund and place a new order. We'll make sure the process is smooth.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Late or Missing Refunds</h2>
        <p>If you haven't received your refund within 7 business days of our confirmation email:</p>
        <ul class="policy-list">
          <li>Check your bank or credit card statement again — sometimes it takes a few extra days to appear.</li>
          <li>Contact your bank or credit card company, as processing times can vary.</li>
          <li>If you've done both and still haven't received your refund, <a href="/pages/contact-us">contact us</a> and we'll sort it out.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Questions?</h2>
        <p>We're here to help. Reach out to us at <strong>support@[brand].com</strong> or visit our <a href="/pages/contact-us">Contact Us</a> page. We want you to feel confident in your purchase — before, during, and after.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

